## 腾讯云

### 操作

1. 添加证书到ssl
2. 在集群对应的命名空间中新建`secret`、
3. 集群创建lb
4. `ssl`证书部署到`tke`对应的`secret`





### 新建`secret`

```
kubectl -n kube-system create secret generic filepax.com \
  --from-literal=qcloud_cert_id=<腾讯云证书ID>
```



### 配置lb

```
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  annotations:
    service.kubernetes.io/qcloud-loadbalancer-type: "internal"  # 指定内网 CLB
    service.kubernetes.io/qcloud-loadbalancer-internal-subnetid: "subnet-7ao0yrl4"  # 必填子网 ID
    service.cloud.tencent.com/direct-access: "true"
    service.cloud.tencent.com/enable-grace-shutdown: "true"
    service.cloud.tencent.com/specify-protocol: '{"80":{"protocol":["HTTP"],"hosts":{"*.filepax.com":{},"*.pikpax.net":{},
      "*.filepax.net":{},"*.pikpakse.com": {}}},
      "443":{"protocol":["HTTPS"],"hosts":{"*.filepax.com":{"tls":
      "filepax.com"}, "*.filepax.net":{"tls": "filepax.net"}, "*.pikpakse.com":{"tls": "pikpakse.com"}, "*.pikpax.net": {"tls":
      "pikpax.net"}}}}'
  name: nginx-ingress-lb-filepax
  namespace: kube-system
spec:
  allocateLoadBalancerNodePorts: true
  externalTrafficPolicy: Local
  internalTrafficPolicy: Cluster
  ipFamilies:
  - IPv4
  ipFamilyPolicy: SingleStack
  ports:
  - name: http
    port: 80
    protocol: TCP
    targetPort: 80
  - name: https
    port: 443
    protocol: TCP
    targetPort: 80
  selector:
    app.kubernetes.io/component: controller
    app.kubernetes.io/instance: ingress-nginx
    app.kubernetes.io/name: ingress-nginx
  sessionAffinity: None
  type: LoadBalancer
```

